Instructions

ViewerY is a lightweight terminal system information tool.
you will need git installed heres how "sudo pacman -S git"

How to use

Clone the repository:
*this is the command to use it only in cd ViewerY*
git clone https://github.com/AlMonDdevV/ViewerY.git
and then do cd ViewerY
then python viewery.py
OR 
cd ViewerY
*this is the command to use it out side cd ViewerY*
then chmod +x viewery.py
then sudo cp viewery.py /usr/local/bin/viewery
sudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/viewery


